Title:

Scope of Career Development and Jobs in Haryana Public Service Commission 

(HPSC)

excerpt :

Among the renowned Public Institutions, the Public Service Commissions are
 
counted among the most significant institutions with long traditions that 

have executed their functions well. The inception and commencement of this
 
institution is originated from the continuous demand of freedom movement  
leaders under the throne of British Raj. The famous notification lies in  
the establishment of the State of Haryana. Moreover, it was under the  
governance of Punjab Re-Organization Act, when the existence of Haryana  
Public Service Commission was realized.
